column5: Hows the ice in big bay ? Would like to get some 1st hand info on ice thickness. Can you get a 4 wheeler ATV out yet ? Looking for a good report c,mon you local guys.
I wouldnt count on it.. I dont even think theyre taking machines out on Cooks Bay on simcoe yet..
My 2 buds just got back from Quinte they drove the truck out fished fri. to tue. am . They caught over 30 walleyes . Said 10" ice where they were fishing.

you can get up to date info herehttp://www.quintefishing.com/ the most consistent ice close to the big lake is near picton telegraph narrows can be hairy in a bad ice year manitoba .... a 100,000 lakes how many walleyes ???? i will never have enough time....
